[29/03/2017 07:18:41] <font color="#ffffff">-Oh, Dios mío.</font>
[29/03/2017 07:18:41] <font color="#ffffff">-Sí.</font>
[29/03/2017 07:18:44] <font color="#ffffff">-Es un jaguar.</font>
[29/03/2017 07:18:44] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Oh, Dios!</font>
