[29/03/2017 21:25:02] <font color="#ffff00">"Imprescindible"</font>
[29/03/2017 21:25:05] <font color="#ffff00">a Luis García Montero?</font>
[29/03/2017 21:25:07] <font color="#ffffff">Es un gran poeta.</font>
